{"tid":2353170,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"(* ✿奈奈分析日誌✿ *) -為上次分析錯誤道歉+重新分析T^T","createTime":"2021-01-04T13:38:20.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-11T05:57:46.000Z","uid":117947,"like":55,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"3635e47adfadb5c531276af7406000f4b476806d","tid":2353170,"uid":117947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T13:38:20.000Z","msg":"經過長時間沉澱,自我檢討,決定重新出發<br />\n上次分析錯誤, 真係萬2分抱歉<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n為此,我決定道歉<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n道歉露出胸部是常識吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過又考慮到連登太多了小朋友<br />\n覺得唔係幾適合咁做,咁都係算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n新既一年,我決定做番個好人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n分析原因有以下:<br />\n<br />\n1.週K突破下降通道<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/foN1DA0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfoN1DA0.png&h=9e7c64e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n結論:升升升<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2.日K突破橫行區間<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kXMBsuk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkXMBsuk.png&h=b26cfec2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n結論:升升升<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n預計升至28000<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3.MACD<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F4GJRV1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF4GJRV1.png&h=d34aa546&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n結論:升升升<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n4.MA<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kRRE9HG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkRRE9HG.png&h=27bb381f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n結論:升升升<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n5.W形態<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ky3sy9m.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKy3sy9m.png&h=dc94bb01&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n結論:升升升<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n預計升至29500<br />\n<br />\n6.資金流入<br />\n過去5日全部流入多過流出<br />\n頭十大成交, 頭9隻都係買入<br />\n個宦買貨, 個市邊有可能跌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自己上網睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.warrants.com/tc/stock/stock-connect/top10-underlying-fundflow\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.warrants.com%2Ftc%2Fstock%2Fstock-connect%2Ftop10-underlying-fundflow&d=zT4eWHrghymhx70gWSuuOcg1Od0Dt6CGL4wHSLmh2%2Bg%3D&h=f0fdd7c6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.warrants.com/tc/stock/stock-connect/top10-underlying-fundflow</a><br />\n結論:升升升<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n預計升至30000<br />\n<br />\n7.即市好友力量<br />\n 其實大家都發覺<br />\n即市只要跌100點, 甚至可能只係幾十點<br />\n隔一陣就會升番突晒<br />\n跌100,升番400<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可見好友力量十分強勁<br />\n結論:升升升<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n目標<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />保守型-28000<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />進取型-29500至30000<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />耐性型-33000<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YB19NHg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYB19NHg.png&h=9f139ca7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-small\">利申:持有少量牛證</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc6684f866b7e79c9709362f6a1fb3162a139aec","tid":2353170,"uid":73241,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T13:38:38.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/42.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b00c2625f48ca954719bebe598bd32a6f0a57fa","tid":2353170,"uid":60556,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T13:39:56.000Z","msg":"多謝你出post救我張put <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12b54d29c2dc6272ce82178642c323d1e6b1456e","tid":2353170,"uid":912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T13:40:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b4faa22d9825179ff9aeddf5987400b9ece0be0","tid":2353170,"uid":117947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3b00c2625f48ca954719bebe598bd32a6f0a57fa","tid":2353170,"uid":60556,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T13:39:56.000Z","msg":"多謝你出post救我張put <img src=\"/asse